    "# HBV-IT miRNA Analysis — Step 3: Literature Meta-Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "**Goal**: Systematically aggregate published HBV miRNA studies to identify  \n",
    "consensus IT-associated miRNAs and build a concordance evidence matrix.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Strategy**:\n",
    "1. Systematic literature database (structured from PubMed search)\n",
    "2. Concordance analysis: direction + statistical significance across studies\n",
    "3. Cross-reference with Step 2 IT-candidate miRNAs\n",
    "4. Final priority tier assignment\n",
    "\n",
    "**Connection to v18 manuscript**: miRNAs targeting AIM2/LGALS9/TGFB1/SOCS1/DNMT1\n",
    "are flagged as potential mechanistic bridges to the 6-layer effector suppression framework."
